{
  "stem": "7093.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And therefore, when later on when it's, when it came to winter and we had beautiful snow, I used to slip out of the barrack at night and strip and wash myself in snow because I felt that it was incredibly necessary, absolutely necessary to, to, to, to be clean, to keep oneself clean.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I mean I could have been shot at the spot that I came out of the barrack, which I was not supposed to come out of at night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But nobody did anything to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I felt a bit cleaner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We, in Hessisch Lichtenau, we also got some underwear.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And people got shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Now I didn't get shoes because I always had very large feet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And unfortunately, the shoes they brought were not large enough.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They were, I don't know, up to 6.5 or maximum 7 or something like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I had size 8 shoe, size 8 feet, or size 9 feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In those days I think it was size 9.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Today it's a bit less.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And therefore.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "There were no shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "There were occasionally there were clogs, which I was given.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And the clogs had-- and occasionally, most of the time, with the clog, I also got a duster to put around my foot, to put into when I wear the clogs.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But I had one roommate who always made it sure that my duster after the first night disappeared from under my head or wherever I hid it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She always managed to find it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And clogs were rather hard on, on bare feet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And were even harder-- and I mean, they broke very soon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So most of the time actually, summer and winter, I was barefoot, and in the snow as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I must take a minute break.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
